functions.name: v8_Default_embedded_blob_code_
functions.logic: Defines an empty array of bytes to represent the embedded code blob.  It's initialized with a single byte set to 0.

functions.name: v8_Default_embedded_blob_code_size_
functions.logic: Defines the size of the embedded code blob array.  It's initialized to 0, indicating an empty blob.

functions.name: v8_Default_embedded_blob_data_
functions.logic: Defines an empty array of bytes to represent the embedded data blob.  It's initialized with a single byte set to 0.

functions.name: v8_Default_embedded_blob_data_size_
functions.logic: Defines the size of the embedded data blob array.  It's initialized to 0, indicating an empty blob.
